This is README file for Algorithm PA#1
Author: Kao, Shao-Fang (Christine 高紹芳) B02901035 電機五
Date: March 20th, 2018
=====
SYNOPSIS:

NTUsort -[IS|MS|HS] <input_file_name> <output_file_name>

This program supports three different sorting methods: insertion sort, merge sort and heap sort.
=====
DIRECTORY:

bin/	<binary code destination>

doc/	b02901035_pa1_report.pdf
		pa1.pdf

inputs/ <all the given input files>

lib/	<library files>

src/	<all my source code>

utility/<validation checkers>

makefile
README

======
HOW TO COMPILE:

To compile, simply follow the following steps
	make

======
HOW TO RUN:

	./bin/NTU_sort -[IS|MS|HS] <input_file_name> <output_file_name>

	For example,
	./bin/NTU_sort -MS inputs/1000.ac.in outputs/1000.ac.MS.out
